\large\frac{m_{t}}{p_{t}} \ = \ \frac{m_{d}/m_s}{p_d/p_s}\; = \; \frac{m_{d}}{p_d} \cdot \frac{p_s}{m_s} 
= \frac{2p_d}{p_d}\cdot \frac{p_s}{\frac 43 p_s}\tag{substitution (1), (2)}
 = 2\cdot \frac{1}{4/3} =  \frac 32\tag{cancel units and evaluate}
